{"inkVersion":20,"root":[["^Good day, Mr. Anderson. I'm Detective White. ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Detective, how may I assist you? ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I am investigating the incidents that have occurred recently. ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^I understand you had a role in the events leading up to Ms. Palmer's death. ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Can you elaborate on your actions? ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Yes, of course. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I was rather displeased with the food last evening. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^So, I decided to take it up with the captain. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I went to the bridge along with Beatrice, the maid. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^That would be when you lodged your complaint about the quality of food? ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Precisely. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^We requested the captain to have a word with the chef. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Beatrice went to fetch Chef Sullivan. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^But as I understand, you didn't wait for her to return? ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^No, Detective. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^When Beatrice didn't return for a while, I decided to go find her myself. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^But you didn't find her or Chef Sullivan, did you? ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Actually, on my way, I ran into Mrs. Jenkins. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^She told me her husband required my presence for some unfinished business. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^So I went to their room. ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n",{"->":"Knot1"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"Knot1":[["ev","str","^About the merchant","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^About the family","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","^I would also like to discuss the unfortunate passing of Mr. Jenkins.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^I understand you've worked closely with him for many years?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Yes, Detective.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I've been at Mr. Jenkins' side for over a decade.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^He was more than just a boss to me.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^His death... it's devastating.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^My condolences, Mr. Anderson.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Can you recall the events of last night?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^When did you last see Mr. Jenkins alive?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^After our business meeting, I left him in his chambers.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^The mistress was with him.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I did not see him after that.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Did anything seem off to you last night?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Any signs of distress or unusual behavior?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Now that you mention it, Mr. Jenkins did seem a bit perturbed after dinner.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^But I thought it was just his typical displeasure with the food.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n",{"->":"Knot1"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["\n","^Mr. Anderson, could you shed some light on the other members of Mr. Jenkins' family?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Of course, Detective.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Arthur, the elder son, is ambitious and driven, very much like his father.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^He's been involved in the family business from a young age.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^And the younger son, Jonathan?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Jonathan is quite different.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^He's an introvert, keeps to himself mostly.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^He's got a knack for chemistry though.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I see.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^I also want to tell you that it may be possible that Chef Sullivan isn't our culprit.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Oh! That's surprising.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: shocked"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^But who else could it be?  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^That's what I'm trying to find out.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^You said Jonathan has a knack for chemistry.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Could he possibly have access to poisons?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Well, now that you mention it, it is possible.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^His studies often involve dealing with different chemical compounds.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^He would have knowledge about poisons.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Mr. Anderson, can you speak more about Jonathan's relationship with his family?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^I must say, Detective, it's not a good one.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^There's been a lot of resentment, especially after Mr. Jenkins remarried.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^He always felt overlooked in favor of his older brother Arthur.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^So there's a possible motive there?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^It's quite possible, Detective.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Jonathan has always been unhappy.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Perhaps it drove him to commit this terrible act.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: sad"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^And how about Beatrice, the maid?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^You mentioned she delivered food to Mr. Jenkins.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Yes, Beatrice has been serving the family for quite a long time.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^She does take meals to Mr. Jenkins, but I find it hard to believe she'd poison him.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: explaining"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Does she have a reason to?  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: thinking"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Not that I'm aware of, Detective.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^She's been loyal to the family, kept to her duties.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^I see no motive.  ",{"#":"speaker: Phillip_Anderson"},{"#":"portrait: neutral"},{"#":"layout: right"},"\n","^Thank you, Mr. Anderson.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: happy"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^These insights provide further avenues to explore.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: happy"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n","^Your cooperation is greatly appreciated.  ",{"#":"speaker: Oliver_White"},{"#":"portrait: happy"},{"#":"layout: left"},"\n",{"->":"Knot1"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}